#. Type: string
#. Description
#: ../lilo-installer.templates:29
msgid "LILO installation target:"
msgstr "Targed sefydliad LILO:"

#. Type: string
#. Description
#: ../lilo-installer.templates:29
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Please enter the partition or disk onto which LILO should be installed. "
"Devfs style names, such as those that start with /dev/ide, /dev/scsi, and /"
"dev/discs are accepted, as well as traditional names, such as /dev/hda or /"
"dev/sda."
msgstr ""
"Os gwelwch yn dda, rhowch y rhaniad neu'r disk lle dylid sefydlu LILO iddo. "
"Derbynnir enwau yn ffurf devfs, megis rheiny yn cychwyn gyda /dev/ide, /dev/"
"scsi a /dev/discs, yn ogystal ag enwau traddodiadol megis /dev/hda neu /dev/"
"sda."

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../lilo-installer.templates:37
msgid "Invalid partition name"
msgstr "Enw rhaniad annilys"

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../lilo-installer.templates:37
msgid ""
"The path ${path} does not represent a partition or hard disk device. Please "
"try again."
msgstr ""
"Nid yw'r llwybr ${path} yn cynreichioli rhaniad neu ddyfais disgen galed. "
"Ceisiwch eto os gwelwch yn dda."

